  <description><![CDATA[<div class="data-grid" style="float: center;">
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 50px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td height="20" align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #89aa4d; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px;">To book our Slovenia Multi-Centre Holidays, please call our reservations team on 01483 79 11 11</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div> </div>
<p>Discover Slovenia by combining the contrasting resorts we feature. Combine the cultural city of <a data-udi="umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5cfd5f91c1d0419185792bc414ff7721}" title="Ljubljana">Ljubljana</a> and enjoy the restaurants and great nightlife with a relaxing stay in the beautiful resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e0872feec9b24b8db1b30d83108b172e}" title="Lake Bled">Lake Bled</a> and visit the only island in <a data-udi="umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb90f98d70e84089a8cb145d8e46e049}" title="Slovenia">Slovenia</a>. Or head to the mountains and the wonderful resorts of <a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab}" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a> and Lake Bohinj. Kranjska Gora has stunning views towards the Julian Alps and the distant peaks of the Karavanke mountains. <a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a> is famous for its crystal clear waters and is the source of the mighty River Soca. </p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Multi Centre Combinations</h2>
<ul>
<li>All resorts can be combined for 3, 4 or 7 night stays</li>
<li>All transfers will be direct between resorts except Ljubljana which will operate via the airport. Transfers are on Wednesdays and Saturdays only</li>
<li>If combining with Austria your transfer will be via Salzburg airport</li>
<li>You can create a 2 to 4 centre holiday. For example, 4 nights + 3 nights + 4 nights + 3 nights to create a 14 night 4 centre holiday</li>
<li>Prices include flights, accommodation, transfer and meals as specified</li>
</ul>
<p>Shown below are some of the most popular combinations, but other resorts and hotel combinations are possible. Other combinations are possible. Please call our reservations team on 01483 79 11 11 to book these holidays.</p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Popular Combinations, departure days &amp; prices for 2019</strong></p>
<p><br /><strong>Lake Bled, Slovenia &amp; Kitzbühel, Austria – 10 nights (depart Wednesday): 7 nights Lake Bled / 3 nights Kitzbühel</strong></p>
<p><strong>Standard accommodation:</strong><strong> Lake Bled</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/093bbc54785244aa9aa802856c0b18e8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/093bbc54785244aa9aa802856c0b18e8}" title="Grand Hotel Toplice">Grand Hotel Toplice</a>) - <strong>Kitzbühel</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/dcecccebd4fc4260b26e10a4cdbe9071" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dcecccebd4fc4260b26e10a4cdbe9071}" title="Hotel Schweizerhof">Hotel Schweizerhof</a>). Price from <strong>£1,119</strong> per person including flights, accommodation on half board and all transfers.</p>
<p>Please note: Transfers will be via Salzburg Airport and Slovenian resorts must be taken as the first centre.</p>
<p><br /><strong>Triglav National Park &amp; Ljubljana</strong></p>
<p><strong>10 nights (depart Wednesday): 3 nights Kranjska Gora / 4 nights Lake Bohinj / 3 nights Ljubljana</strong></p>
<p><strong>Standard accommodation:</strong><strong> Kranjska Gora</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642}" title="Best Western Hotel Kranjska Gora (formerly Hotel Lek)">Best Western Hotel</a>) - <strong>Lake Bohinj</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/e06cfb2dd33f494e88ac01de07d9193e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e06cfb2dd33f494e88ac01de07d9193e}" title="Hotel Kristal">Hotel Kristal</a>) - <strong>Ljubljana </strong>(<a data-udi="umb://document/111ec8e021f2424b903c4064fa0f81a1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/111ec8e021f2424b903c4064fa0f81a1}" title="City Hotel">Hotel City</a>). Price from <strong>£1,520</strong> per person including flights, accommodation on half board and all transfers.</p>
<p><strong>Standard accommodation:</strong><strong> Kranjska Gora</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba}" title="Hotel Kompas">Hotel Kompas</a>) - <strong>Lake Bohinj</strong> (<a data-udi="umb://document/2aeb8216bf2947b9951b9a65f072cf51" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2aeb8216bf2947b9951b9a65f072cf51}" title="Hotel Jezero">Hotel Jezero</a> - superior room) - <strong>Ljubljana </strong>(<a data-udi="umb://document/51e302ae36974ff886e822c3ad409e09" href="/{localLink:umb://document/51e302ae36974ff886e822c3ad409e09}" title="Best Western Hotel Slon">Hotel Slon</a>). Price from <strong>£1,735</strong> per person including flights, accommodation on half board and all transfers.</p>
<p>Please note: Transfers will be via Salzburg Airport.</p>
<p> </p>
<p style="font-size: 21px;"><strong>Departure flights from:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>• Gatwick, Manchester &amp; Stansted</li>
<li>• Flight supplements may apply</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
